<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.4">
<l>nīrmali kiṉṟatōr mīṉāyō rāmaiyumāy</l>
<l>cīrmali kiṉṟatōr ciṅka vuruvāki</l>
<l>kārmali vaṇṇaṉkaṇ ṇapurat temperumāṉ</l>
<l>tārmali taṇṭuḻāy tāḻntūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, alight and sip the fresh, abounding tulasī garland</l>
<l>On him who is the color of abounding clouds, our great lord of Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l>Having become a fish and having become a turtle</l>
<l rend="indent">[with] the abounding of the waters,</l>
<l> Having become a lion’s form [with] the abounding of goodness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
